Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:23.67,Default,,0,0,373,,本字幕僅用於學習交流，禁止一切商業用途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.23,0:00:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26}導演      編劇\N亞歷桑德羅·佐杜洛夫斯基
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26}現實之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}金錢如同血液\NMoney is like blood,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}流動之時賦予生命\Nit gives life if it flows.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}金錢如同基督\NMoney is like Christ,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}分享之時受到祝福\Nit blesses you if you share it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}金錢如同佛陀\NMoney is like Buddha,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你若不行履\Nif you don't work,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}就無法懂得\Nyou don't get it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}金錢啟示那些使用它的\N{\i1}Money enlightens those who use it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}以開啟世界之花\N{\i1}to open the flower of the world,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}詛咒那些膜拜它的人\N{\i1}and damns those who glorify it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}混淆富足與靈魂\N{\i1}confounding riches with the soul.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}毫無差異\N{\i1}There is no difference{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}金錢與意識毫無差異\N{\i1}between money and conscience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}意識與死亡毫無差異\N{\i1}There is no difference\Nbetween conscience and death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}死亡與財富毫無差異\N{\i1}There is no difference\Nbetween death and wealth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你這混帳為何總這麼羞怯？\NWhy the hell are you so shy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}感知那個孩子吧，困陷於你胸口的孩子，\N{\i1}Feeling the child\Ntrapped within your breast,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}眼中滿是永恒的迷失.\N{\i1}the eyes full of an eternal absence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}一直是局外人，永恒的局外人.\N{\i1}Always outsiders, eternal outsiders.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,叫了你你就跟過來！\NCome when you're told!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊{\u1}傑{\u0}！\NHello Jaime!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見啦！\NIt's been ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,商鋪經營得順利麽？\NEverything alright in the shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你那宏偉的{\u1}烏克蘭小屋{\u0}！\NThe Gran Casa Ukrania!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你想念我們了麽？\NDo you miss us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你想了！\NI bet you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你依舊那樣強壯麽？\NAre you still just as strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得呢？\NWhat do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你兒子知不知道你曾是這裏的攀繩高手？\NDoes your son know\Nyou used to climb ropes here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你現在還能行麽？\NCan you still do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,當然行！\NOf course I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們看看，眼見才為實.\NLet us see, as the blind say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-走！看看去！\N-閉嘴，你這死胖子！\N- Let us go!\N- Shut up, you old fatso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,現實，現實之舞！\NReality, the dance of reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們看看你能做些什麽！\NLet us see what you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,爬呀！向上！\NUP you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我能行！\NI can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你依舊保持著你那迷人的肌肉！\NYou still have your lovely muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但你强力的拳頭，我懷疑它！\NBut your mighty fists, I doubt it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,記得你向觀眾挑戰拳擊麽？\NRemember you challenged\Nthe audience to box you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我當然記得！\NOf course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,打倒他，他們就能得到賞金.\NThey got cash\Nif they beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，但兩擊之內，他就能將他們放倒在地.\NYes, but with two blows\Nhe would lay them flat on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如今你在銷售熱褲，\NNow that you sell knickers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你還能做到麼？\Ncan you still do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,當然可以.\NOf course I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們套上拳套.\NLet us put on the gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,拳套？\NGloves?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:05:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,赤手空拳幹吧，像男人一樣！\NBare fists, like men!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣爸爸，他們會殺了你的.\NDon't,Papa. They'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴，你這懦夫！他們會說我兒子是個娘娘腔.\NShut up, you coward!\NThey'll say my son is a queer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小心點！我們會吃了你！\NWatch out!\NWe're going to eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐，眞是噩夢！\NOh, horror!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}傑{\u0}打了我！\NJaime hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我要昏倒了.\NI'm going to faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}胡蘿蔔{\u0}，{\u1}胡蘿蔔{\u0}！\NCarrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-我好害怕！\N-害怕？\N- I'm scared!\N- Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-永遠不准你這麼說！\N-他在害怕！\N- Don't ever say that!\N- He's scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1\i1}托科皮亞{\u0}，在這里顫抖，\N{\i1}Tocopilla, this tremor,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}這里岩石的味道，\N{\i1}this scent of stones,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}這個小鎮的挽歌\N{\i1}this lament of a small town{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}被陽光撕裂成碎片，\N{\i1}torn to shreds by the sun,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}那些患病的街道\N{\i1}those patient streets{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}渴望著哪怕一顆水滴.\N{\i1}longing for a drop of water.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}烏克蘭小屋{\u0}！\NCasa Ukrania!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨{\u1}烏克蘭小屋{\u0}！\NWelcome to Casa Ukrania!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,進來快進來！\NCome on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}亞歷桑德羅{\u0}！\NAlejandrito!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麽要跑掉，我的父親？\NWhy are you running, my dear father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是妳的父親！我是你兒子！\NI'm not your father! I'm your son!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}亞歷桑德羅{\u0}！\NAlejandrito!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,瘋吧！\NGet mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,瘋吧！\NGet mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是同性戀！\NI am not a faggot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你嚇不到我！\NYou don't scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,隨你變得多麼龐大！\NGet as big as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了夠了，傻孩子！\NThat's enough, silly child!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-放開我，你這老酒鬼！\N-夠了！\N- Let me go, you old drunk!\N- Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一個小小的石子就足以殺死\NA single stone can kill
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大海中所有的游鱼.\Nall the fish in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我，聖杯的女皇，如是說.\NSo say I, the Queen of Cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我！\NLet me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃吧！\NRun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你這個小兇手！\NYou murdering child!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你折磨大海，它們都被你殺光了！\NBy torturing the sea you killed them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,快滾開,你這個老巫婆！\NGet lost, you old hag!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我感到困惑.\N{\i1}I felt confused:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我是應該承受這些沙丁魚的痛苦？\N{\i1}should I suffer the anguish\Nof the sardines{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}還是應該為海鷗的愉悅而感到欣喜{\i0}？\N{\i1}or should I delight\Nin the joy of the gulls.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}當我看到海鷗掠奪著它們的盛宴，\N{\i1}The balance tipped\Nin favour of anguish{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}平衡傾斜了，偏向于痛苦的一方.\N{\i1}when I saw the seagulls\Ndeprived of their banquet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在那個世界，那個讓我覺得自己像個陌生人的世界,\N{\i1}In that world,\Nin which I felt a stranger,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}一切事物都緊密相聯，\N{\i1}all things were connected{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:09:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}聯繫在苦難與歡愉交織的網絡之中.\N{\i1}in a web of suffering\Nand pleasure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋！肉桂和香草口味的冰淇淋！\NIce cream! Cinnamon and vanilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.11,Default,,0,0,350,,華爾街的崩潰\NThe collapse of Wall Street
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:22.66,Default,,0,0,350,,使70%的智利人陷入貧窮.\Nhas impoverished 70% of the Chileans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:26.54,Default,,0,0,350,,我們的總統，上校{\u1}卡洛斯·伊瓦涅斯·德爾坎波{\u0}\NOur president, Colonel Carlos Ibáñez del Campo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:29.16,Default,,0,0,350,,宣佈國家公庫\Ndeclares that the Public Treasury
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:32.13,Default,,0,0,350,,正處於空前難遇的發展基點.\Nhas never been on a better footing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:35.88,Default,,0,0,350,,不久，會為所有民眾提供就業崗位.\NSoon there will be employment for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這些撒謊的暴發戶！\NYou lying jumped-up private!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,行行好，年輕人，我只是想在這裡撓撓背可以麼？\NIf you allow me, young man,\NI'll just scratch my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,願意讓我幫你撓嗎？\NWould you like me to do it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊，如果我沒惹你反感.\NWell, if I don't disgust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,吃掉我的冰淇淋吧，如果我也沒惹你反感的話~\NFinish my ice cream,\Nif I don't disgust you either!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,別這麼說！我很高興~\NCome on! It would be a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,弄疼你了嗎？\NAm I hurting you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,自從我因礦難失去了手臂\NSince I lost my hands in the mine
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,美國佬就把我趕了出去，再沒有人碰過我.\Nand the Yanks kicked me out,\Nno one has touched me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可憐人.\NPoor man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你這個骯髒的廢人，\NYou dirty cripple,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,過來，你該被關進監獄！\Ncome back, and you'll go to jail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸，是我要求給他撓背的.\NI offered to scratch his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-他自己做不到！\N-給我閉嘴！\N- He can't do it!\N- Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,別讓這種穢物靠近你！\NDon't let this filth come near you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他們滿身都是虱子！\NThey're full of lice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你做派像{\u1}斯大林{\u0}一樣？\NWhy dress up like Stalin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,明明說自己是共產主義者，卻只尊重金錢.\NYou say you're a communist\Nbut you only respect the rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我有錢，你肯定會親吻我的殘肢！\NIf I had money, you'd kiss my stumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,操蛋的猶太人！婊子養的！\NYou fucking Jew! Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,滾遠點！\NFuck off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,要是敢再來，我打斷你的狗腿！\NIf you come back, I'll cut your legs off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-你這王八蛋！\N{\u1}傑{\u0}，讓他走吧！\N- Motherfucker!\N- Jaime, let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛要安撫那個廢人？\NWhy hug that cripple?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡男人，是嗎！？\NYou like men, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就憑這一頭娘娘腔的鬃毛，\NWith that girlish mane,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我們對你還能有什麼指望？\Nwhat else could we expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這頭髮讓他看上去像個同性戀！\NWith that hair, he looks like a faggot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,對他放尊重些，\NShow him some respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}亞歷桑德羅{\u0}是聖潔的.\NAlejandro is holy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,聖潔，真是一派胡言！\NHoly, my bollocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴他你為什麼叫他父親而不是兒子！\NTell him why you call him your father\Nand not your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,現在就告訴他！\NTell him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在俄羅斯，\NIn Russia,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我的母親墜入了愛河，\Nmy mother fell in love
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,愛上了我的父親，\Nwith my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一位英俊的俄羅斯舞者.\Na handsome Russian dancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,為了逃離\NThey were on the run
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,憎恨猶太民族的哥薩克人.\Nfrom the Jew-hating Cossacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我父母移居到了阿根廷，\NThey emigrated to Argentina
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裡他們辛勤地耕作\Nwhere they worked hard to cultivate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,屬於自己的一小塊土地.\Na small piece of land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,為點燃一盞油燈，我的父親\NTo light a lamp, my father
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,攀上了一個\Nclimbed on to a cask
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,盛滿酒精的木桶.\Nof alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,桶蓋在他體重的壓迫下碎裂了.\NThe lid broke under his weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他被活生生燒死在那裡.\NHe was burned alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,當我懷上了身孕，\NWhen I got pregnant,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:13:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你就是\NI knew you would be
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我父親的輪迴轉世.\Nmy father reincarnated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣，\NAnd so it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你誕生了，有著同樣厚實的金髮.\Nyou were born with the same thick blond hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這把梳子\NThis comb
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是唯一一件我父親的遺物.\Nis the only thing that remains of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了！\NEnough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,唬人的童話！\NFairy tales!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,兒子就是兒子！\NYour son is your son!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你這些無理取鬧會把他搞瘋的！\NYou'll drive him crazy with this nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不要帶走他！他是我的！\NDon't take him away! He's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢！\NJust try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,向我道歉.\NApologise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起.\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}烏克蘭小屋{\u0}！{\u1}烏克蘭小屋{\u0}！\NCasa Ukrania!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,做掉高價！\NDown with high prices!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你來啦，操蛋的猶太人！\NThere you are, fucking Jew!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我告訴過你別再來的！\NI told you not to come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,求你別這樣，爸爸！\NPlease don't, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,放手！\NLet go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那個猶太人打了我！\NThat's the Jew who hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,過來你這個混球！老屁眼！\NC'mon you jerk! Asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,蟑螂！蟑螂！烹調蟑螂！\NCockroach! Cooking cockroach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,墓穴！墓碑！葬在墓內！\NThe tomb and the tombstone!\NEntombed in the tomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,炸藥！欠操的肥婊子！\NThe dynamite! Fucking fat bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都沒給我們！還把我們炸碎！\NBlows us apart! Gives us but nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,蟑螂！蟑螂！烹調蟑螂了！\NCockroach! Cooking cockroach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,墓穴！墓碑！葬在墓內啊！\NThe tomb and the tombstone!\NEntombed in the tomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,炸藥！欠操的肥婊子！\NThe dynamite! Fucking fat bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都沒予我們！還把我們炸碎！\NBlows us apart!\NGives us but nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他們砍掉了我們的腿，\NThey cut off our legs,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他們砍掉了我們的臂！\NThey cut off our arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,炸藥沒有心靈，\NDynamite has no heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,它輕輕地將我們撕爛,\NIt strokes us apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,炸藥沒有心靈.\NDynamite has no heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,它輕輕地將我們扯爛,\NIt strokes us apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,傻逼！婊子養的！\NFucking jerk! Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你是這樣一個懦夫！？\NHow can you be such a coward?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不許亂動！\NKeep still!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽會生氣的！\NMy mother will be angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你外表像一個娼婦，而不是一個男人.\NYou look like a whore, not like a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,安份點，否則我把你的頭髮扯下來！\NCalm down or I'll tear your hair out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,開始吧.\NGo ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎麼了，小矮子？\N-很疼.\N- What's the matter, midget?\N- It really hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:16:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,別為不屬於自己的東西感到痛苦.\NDon't suffer for what isn't yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你祖父的頭髮.\NIt's your grandfather's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這妄想該結束了！\NEnough of this delusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走.\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:17:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以開始學學如何做一個男人了！\NNow you'll learn how to be a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你兒子回來了！\NHere is your son!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你金色的捲髮呢？\NYour golden curls?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰？\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不認識你.\NI don't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,叛徒！\NTraitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,永遠別再碰我！\NDon't ever touch me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫你走開！\NI'm telling you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你和{\u1}傑{\u0}...\NYou and Jaime...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,殺害了我的父親！\Nhave murdered my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你離我而去\NYou've left me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我成了孤兒.\Nan orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,顧客登門她就會出來的.\NShe'll come out for the customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,高價消費去死吧！\NDeath to high prices!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嘗嘗這個！還有這個！\NTake that! And that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不准動.\NStay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,男人懂得自我控制！\NA man controls himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我撓你的腳心.\NI'm going to tickle you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是不笑，才配做我的兒子.\NIf you don't laugh,\Nyou deserve to be my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不准笑！\NDon't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,很好.\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,腋窩.\NThe armpits!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不准屈服！\NDon't give in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來是脖頸.\NNow the neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,堅持住.\NResist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,鼻子.\NThe nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧.\NAlright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你開始贏得我的欽佩了.\NYou're starting to deserve my admiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,別高興太早，\NDon't look so happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是說“開始”.\NI only said "starting to".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果想我為你驕傲，\NIf you want me to be proud of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,必須向我展示，你可以承受住痛苦.\Nyou must show me you can deal with pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來我要扇你耳光.\NI'm going to slap you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,聽你要求，我會加大力度.\NIf you ask me to, I'll slap you harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你越是要我扇，\NAnd the more you ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.98,0:19:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我就扇得越重.\Nthe harder I'll slap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我們看看你能應付多久.\NWe'll see how much you can cope with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,開始吧.\NLet's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,重點.\NHarder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,再重點.\NHarder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,再重點.\NHarder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,再重點.\NHarder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,再重點.\NHarder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,再重點.\NHarder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你打掉了我的牙，\NYou broke my tooth,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可是如果你愛我，這不算什麼要緊事.\Nbut if you love me, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這當然要緊.\NOf course it matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,走，去看牙醫.\NTo the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,上車，你們這幫懶惰的混球！\NGet on, you lazy bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,開去垃圾堆！\NTo the rubbish dump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,炸藥沒有心靈，\NDynamite has no heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:21:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,它輕輕地將我們撕扯爛.\NIt strokes us apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴張大，孩子.\NOpen wide, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,唾液沾到空氣會很疼.\NThe air on the saliva must hurt a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,男人必須勇敢.\NA man must be brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果按我說得做，\NIf you do as I ask
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你會贏得我的欽佩.\Nthen you will win my admiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,治療過程中別讓他涂麻藥.\NLet him treat you without anaesthetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著.\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,意志能夠克服疼痛.\NWillpower overcomes pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們瞧瞧你像不像我.\NLet's see if you are like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:22:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴張大，這只是一針止痛劑.\NOpen wide. It's just a little painkiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不必注射，{\u1}胡里奧{\u0}先生.\NNo injection, Don Julio.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他會很疼的.\NBut it will really hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我給你兩瓶紅酒.\NI'll send you two bottles of wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你說呢孩子？\NWhat does the boy have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要注射，先生.\NI don't need an injection, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，既然你這麼說了.\NWell, if you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.32,0:22:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,張大你的嘴.\NOpen your mouth wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.64,0:23:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,行了，孩子. 全部完工.\NThat's it, son. All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你是個真正的英雄！\NYou're a real hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你做到了...\NYou did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有啜泣.\Nwithout a whimper!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有顫抖.\NWithout trembling!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.24,0:23:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有落淚.\NWithout a tear!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你是{\u1}佐杜洛夫斯基{\u0}的一員！\NYou are a Jodorowsky!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.71,0:23:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧.\NCome here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.58,0:23:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了突然？\NNow what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,別像個女孩一樣！\NDon't be such a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我兒子！站起來混蛋！\NYou're my son!\NStand up, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我絆倒了，爸爸，我沒事.\NI tripped, Papa, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這才是我的孩子.\NThat's my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.99,0:23:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,意志能夠克服一切.\NWillpower overcomes all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,再見，{\u1}胡里奧{\u0}先生，謝謝你.\NSee you, Don Julio. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.35,0:23:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我會帶酒給你來的.\NI'll send you the bottles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.73,0:23:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-要法國紅酒，{\u1}傑{\u0}先生.\N-好.\N- Make it French wine, Don Jaime.\N- Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋，冰淇淋，冰淇淋.\NIce cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.76,0:23:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,地，水，火，風四種口味.\N{\i1}Water, air, earth and fire flavours!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你非常努力，兒子.\NYou made a great effort, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.80,0:24:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，爸爸.\NYes, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.17,0:24:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你該去呼吸一下海風.\NYou need to breathe some sea air.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.59,0:24:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,會舒服許多.\NYou'll feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.22,0:24:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，爸爸.\NYes, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.91,0:24:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須回店里了.\NI have to get back to the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.12,0:24:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,待在這兒看看大海吧.\NStay here and look at the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.65,0:25:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，孩子！\NHey, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.60,0:25:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你勇敢嗎？\NAre you brave?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.09,0:25:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,當然！\NYes, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.97,0:25:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那你等在那兒.\NThen wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.28,0:25:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怕了嗎？\NAre you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.65,0:25:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒有，聖徒.\NNo, Theosophist.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.93,0:25:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-為什麼不怕？\N-我是個男人，聖徒.\N- Why not?\N- I'm a man, Theosophist.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.00,0:25:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-你知道我？\N-是的.\N- You know my name?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.46,0:25:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-誰告訴了你我的事？\N-我爸爸.\N- Who told it to you?\N- My papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.67,0:25:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈你爸爸.\NYour papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.22,0:25:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,來，我教導你如何冥想.\NLook, I'll show you how to meditate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.56,0:25:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,跟著我念：\NSay after me:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.48,0:25:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,揭諦\NGate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.51,0:25:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,揭諦\NGate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.65,0:25:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,揭諦\NGate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.22,0:25:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,揭諦\NGate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.02,0:25:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,波羅揭諦\NParagate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.14,0:25:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,波羅揭諦\NParagate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.76,0:25:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,波羅僧揭諦\NParasamgate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.40,0:26:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,波羅僧揭諦\NParasamgate.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.80,0:26:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,菩提娑婆訶.\NBodhi Svaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.35,0:26:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,菩提娑婆訶.\NBodhi Svaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.62,0:26:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,揭諦，於知識之中.\NGate, in the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.62,0:26:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,揭諦，於內心之中.\NGate, in the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.16,0:26:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,揭諦，於性別之中.\NGate, in the sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.04,0:26:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,波羅揭諦，還要更深入.\NParagate, even deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.84,0:26:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,波羅僧揭諦，心靈.\NParasamgate, heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.80,0:26:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,菩提娑婆訶，極樂！\NBodhi Svaha, happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.18,0:26:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,菩提娑婆訶，極樂！\NBodhi Svaha, happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.93,0:26:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,菩提娑婆訶，極樂！\NBodhi Svaha, happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.35,0:26:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,極樂，極樂，極樂，\Nhappiness, happiness, happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.48,0:26:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,極樂，極樂！\Nhappiness, happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.90,0:26:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我一起.\NCome with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.83,0:26:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,揭諦揭諦，波羅揭諦，波羅僧揭諦，菩提娑婆訶.\NGate, Gate, Paragate, Parasamgate, Bodhi Svaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.42,0:26:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道這些纜車存在於此地多久了嗎？\NDo you know how long\Nthese cable cars have been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.42,0:27:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不清楚，聖徒.\NI don't know, Theosophist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.96,0:27:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,千萬年億萬年\NThousands and thousands
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.80,0:27:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至億億年.\Nand thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.19,0:27:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本無從得知它們來自何處去向何處，\NYou don't know where they come from\Nnor where they go,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.77,0:27:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但你可以帶走一塊它們的岩石，\Nbut you can take one of their rocks
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.63,0:27:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,并如同寶物一般珍藏它/\Nand keep it like a treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.94,0:27:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,來.\NCome.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.11,0:27:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這些渡船就像我們的肉體，載著我們的靈魂.\NThose oars are like our bodies\Nwhich carry our souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.70,0:27:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,靈魂是一件珍寶，\NThe soul is a treasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.08,0:27:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,神就在我們體內.\Nthe god within us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.92,0:27:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我要給你一件禮物.\NI'm going to give you a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.34,0:27:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,看到這三個勛章了嗎？\NSee these three medals?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.13,0:27:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,它們認為彼此是不同的，分裂的.\NThey think they're separate.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.80,0:27:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,將它們投入熔爐，\NMelt them down in an oven,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.22,0:27:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就會化為單一的液滴.\Nand they will turn into a single drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.85,0:27:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,來，收下它們.\NHere, have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.48,0:28:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,用它們做一串項鏈，\NMake a necklace with them
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.19,0:28:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,時刻佩戴它們以此提醒自己，\Nand wear it all the time to remind you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.24,0:28:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,單純的神能夠統一這三者.\Nthat a single god unites the three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.70,0:28:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你，聖徒.\NThank you, Theosophist.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.74,0:29:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛這個香味.\NI love this perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.81,0:29:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,把飲料放下.\NPut that drink down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.94,0:30:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡它.\NI feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.06,0:30:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜歡.\NI don't feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.21,0:30:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡！\NWell, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.82,0:30:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡誰說了算？\NWho commands here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.07,0:30:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你.\NYou.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.95,0:30:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,過來！\NCome!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.42,0:30:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的！\NYou are mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.74,0:30:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,看我得到了什麼.\NLook what I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.04,0:30:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜點，孩子.\NCalm down, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.07,0:30:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-快看！\N-這是什麼？\N- Look!\N- What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.33,0:31:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,勛章！\NMedals!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.62,0:31:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-誰給你的？\N-聖徒.\N- Who gave them to you?\N- The Theosophist.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.00,0:31:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我告訴過你不准去見他！\NI told you not to see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.71,0:31:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,把這些垃圾給我.\NShow me this rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.89,0:31:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,瘋狂的白癡！\NCrazy idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.64,0:31:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,用虛無的夢麻痺自己對死亡的恐懼！\NNumbing his fear of death\Nwith idle dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.23,0:31:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,跪下.\NOn your knees!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.94,0:31:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,神不存在.\NGod does not exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.44,0:31:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,神不存在.\NGod does not exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.86,0:31:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,神不存在.\NGod does not exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.74,0:31:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,人只有死亡隨後腐爛！\NYou die and you rot!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.62,0:31:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不存在超越於此的事物！\NThere's nothing beyond!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.75,0:31:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你的父親永遠不欺騙你！\NYour father never lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.58,0:31:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信誰，我還是那個白癡？\NWho do you believe, me or that idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.71,0:31:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我該如何選擇？\N{\i1}Who was I going to choose?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.34,0:31:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你，爸爸，那個乞丐瘋了.\NI believe you, Papa. The beggar is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.43,0:31:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,神並不存在，人只有死亡隨後腐爛.\NGod does not exist. You die and you rot.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.39,0:32:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不存在超越於此的事物.\NThere's nothing beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.35,0:32:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好！你可以站起來了.\NBravo! Up you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.56,0:32:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,勇士會戰勝自己編織的謊言.\NA warrior overcomes his delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.19,0:32:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,現在快去睡覺.\NNow go to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.11,0:32:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}每週三，\N{\i1}Every Wednesday,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.07,0:32:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}深夜時分，\N{\i1}late at night,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.16,0:32:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我都會被父親離開家的聲音驚醒，\N{\i1}I awoke and looked on anxiously{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.45,0:32:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}一臉焦慮.\N{\i1}as my father left the house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.46,0:32:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他去了哪裡？\N{\i1}Where was he going?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.97,0:32:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡什麼樣的？\NDo you fancy some?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.43,0:32:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,來吹一個吧，{\u1}傑{\u0}？\NBlowjob, Jaime?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.14,0:32:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,居然在思考永恆的生命.\NThink of the life eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.82,0:32:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,來玩{\u1}樂透{\u0}！來贏一隻雛雞！\NLotto! Win a chick!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.54,0:32:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,來啊，{\u1}蘿莉塔{\u0}.\NCome, Rosita.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.69,0:32:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這是屬於我們的{\u1}托科皮亞{\u0}.\NThis is our Tocopilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.36,0:33:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要為它奉獻些什麼.\NWe have to do something for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.33,0:33:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一場重要的秘密會議.\NI have an important secret meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.91,0:33:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,改天再見，好麼？\NAnother time, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.00,0:33:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}傑{\u0}，你知道我喜歡你，\NJaime, you know I like you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.05,0:33:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我也從不試圖改變你.\Nand I've never charged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.62,0:33:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,安好啊，同志們.\NGreetings, comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.08,0:33:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,安好，同志.\NGreetings, comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.68,0:33:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,壞消息，同志們，我們有危險了.\NBad news, comrades. We're in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.76,0:33:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}伊瓦涅斯{\u0}正在領導一場法西斯專政.\NIbáñez is heading for a fascist dictatorship.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.17,0:34:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,宰殺工人和學生已經滿足不了他了.\NSlaughtering workers\Nand students wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.43,0:34:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,跟隨那些美國銀行家投機也不行.\NNor speculating with Yankee bankers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.77,0:34:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如今，他想要囚禁所有的共產主義者.\NNow, he wants to intern all the communists.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.72,0:34:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著，同志們\NListen, comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.50,0:34:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我的夥伴{\u1}安布羅希亞{\u0}寄給我一封信.\NMy friend Ambrosia\Nhas sent me a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.03,0:34:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,信？\NA letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.97,0:34:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,“親愛的{\u1}托納{\u0}，我有些可怕的消息要告訴你.”\N"Dear Toña,\NI have something dreadful to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.19,0:34:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,“按{\u1}伊瓦涅斯{\u0}命令，\N"On Ibáñez's orders, the police
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.32,0:34:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,警察正在搜捕同性戀并實施溺刑.\N"are drowning the homosexuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.82,0:34:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我的情人，一位將我視作女性的同性戀警察，\N"My lover, a queer cop\Nwho pretends I'm a woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.41,0:34:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,用沉重的鐵鏈捆綁了十名同好，\N"tied ten of them to a heavy chain,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.41,0:34:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,押上飛機將他們拋入大海.\N"put them on a plane\Nand threw them in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.41,0:34:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你和姐妹們的生命都受到了威脅.\N"You and our sisters live under threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.29,0:34:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,小心行事，愛你的，{\u1}安布羅希亞{\u0}.”\N"Take care.\NLove, Ambrosia."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.63,0:34:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,先是共產主義者，\NFirst the communists,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.38,0:34:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然後是同性戀，\Nthen the homosexuals,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.38,0:34:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,再之後是學生，罷工的水手，礦工...\Nthen the students,\Nthe sailors on strike, the miners...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.84,0:34:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要忍耐多久？\NHow long are we going to stand this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.51,0:34:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,多久！？\NYes, how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.35,0:34:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可以組織一場大罷工，\NWe could organise a general strike
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.64,0:34:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,通過傳單，郵件，\Nby means of leaflets, letters
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.06,0:34:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,和秘密集會.\Nand secret meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.44,0:34:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我們如何啟動這一切？\NHow would we fund all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.02,0:34:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我們甚至沒錢購買一杯飲料.\NWe don't even have enough to buy a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.11,0:35:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\u1}托納{\u0}同志.\N-怎麼了，{\u1}傑{\u0}.\N- Comrade Toña?\N- Yes, Jaime.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.44,0:35:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,買些啤酒來吧.\NBring us some beers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.03,0:35:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好樣的，{\u1}佐杜洛夫斯基{\u0}同志！\NBravo, Comrade Jodorowsky!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.70,0:35:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不准稱呼我{\u1}佐杜洛夫斯基{\u0}！\NDon't you Jodorowsky me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.28,0:35:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,同志們，你們知道的，\NComrades, you know full well
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.95,0:35:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我真正的名字只有一個，\Nmy real name is the one
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.70,0:35:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,印在我的共產主義證件上：\Non my communist card:
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.46,0:35:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}胡安·阿勞卡尼亞{\u0}.\NJuan Araucano.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.87,0:35:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，胡安同志.\NSorry, Comrade Juan.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.33,0:35:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,現在起，我們必須像宦官一樣度日，\NFrom now on,\Nwe must live as eunuchs,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.59,0:35:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,撕碎所有證據，\Ndestroy compromising documents
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.88,0:35:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,閉緊自己的嘴巴，直到好日子來臨.\Nand keep our mouths shut\Nuntil we see better days.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.93,0:35:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,說到就要做到.\NNo sooner said than done!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.15,0:35:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就這麼幹吧.\NSo be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.32,0:35:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-別這麼大驚小怪\N-閉嘴，你這婊子.\N- Stop that fuss!\N- Shut up, you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.75,0:35:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-你才是婊子！\N-喂，別這樣.\N- You're a bigger bitch than I am!\N- Come on! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.58,0:35:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我們應該做些什麼，姑娘們，不能就這麼算了.\NWe've got to do something, girls!\NWe can't go on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.05,0:36:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,同志們！\NComrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.21,0:36:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,乾杯！\NCheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.72,0:36:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,乾杯！\NCheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.01,0:36:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界的工人們...\NWorkers of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.85,0:36:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,團結起來！\NUnite!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.14,0:36:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,起來，饑寒交迫的奴隸，\NArise ye workers from your slumbers
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.22,0:36:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,起來，全世界受苦的人.\NArise ye prisoners of want
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.75,0:36:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,乾杯吧，同志們！\NCheers, comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.37,0:36:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,乾杯！\NCheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.21,0:36:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,共產黨萬歲！\NLong live the Communist Party!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.46,0:36:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}烏克蘭小屋{\u0}正在販售紅鼻頭，\NThe Casa Ukrania offers you a red nose
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.92,0:36:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,現在購買九折優惠...\Nand 10% off all purchases...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.52,0:36:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴！\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.72,0:36:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,把那鼻頭摘下來.\NTake off that nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.31,0:36:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-我有個驚喜要給你.\N-是什麼，爸爸？\N- I've got a surprise for you.\N- What, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.73,0:36:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,稍後你就知道.\NYou'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.36,0:37:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,立正！\NAttention!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.53,0:37:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,稍息.\NAt ease!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.33,0:37:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}卡讚{\u0}同志，我們永遠不會忘記你.\NComrade Kazan, we will never forget you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.04,0:37:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我們永遠不會忘記你！\NWe will never forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.21,0:37:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的吉祥物去世了，\NOur mascot has passed away
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.01,0:37:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就在距離我們一年一度的遊行前三天，\Njust three days before our annual parade,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.05,0:37:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不過，我們找到了人來代替他.\Nbut we have found someone to replace him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.22,0:37:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我榮幸地通知你，大家一致讚成，\NI am proud to inform you that everyone agrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.69,0:37:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你，就是{\u1}托科皮亞{\u0}消防隊的新任吉祥物.\NYou are the new mascot\Nof Tocopilla's Fire Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.45,0:37:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想當吉祥物，我又不是狗.\NI don't want to be a mascot. I'm not a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.53,0:37:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這是榮譽，年輕的同志.\NIt is an honour, little comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.79,0:37:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,別的孩子都會嫉妒你.\NThe other children will envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.41,0:38:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-他們會嘲笑我.\N-那也是源於嫉妒.\N- They'll laugh at me!\N- Out of envy!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.96,0:38:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴！\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.22,0:38:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,來，穿上它.\NHere, put it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.97,0:38:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你會像個英雄.\NYou'll look a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.65,0:38:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.97,0:38:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你給我那個黑人穿的鞋子.\NI will if you give me\Nthe black man's shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.06,0:38:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼黑人？哪一雙鞋？\NWhat black man? What shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.10,0:38:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那雙商店櫥窗里人偶穿著的紅鞋.\NThe red shoes of the dummy in the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.06,0:38:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人偶非常昂貴.\NThat automaton was very expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.32,0:38:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,它一定要裝扮高雅.\NIt has to be elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.86,0:38:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,要是赤著腳，人們會怎樣議論它？\NWhat will people say\Nif it's barefoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.15,0:38:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,給它穿我的鞋子不就好了.\NPut him in my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.24,0:38:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-這雙鞋多醜陋！\N-是你買的！\N- They're ugly!\N- You bought them!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.53,0:38:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我從來不買醜陋的東西.\NI don't buy ugly things.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.24,0:38:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？\NWell then?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.96,0:38:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，你說服了我.\NAlright then. You've persuaded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.25,0:38:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以擁有它們.\NYou can have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.43,0:39:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.31,0:39:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}卡利托斯{\u0}！\NCarlitos!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.56,0:39:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,看，我得到一雙新鞋！\NLook, I've got new shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.07,0:39:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我從來沒見過這麼漂亮的鞋子.\NThey're the most beautiful shoes\NI've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.61,0:39:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯！\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.06,0:39:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼哭了？\NWhy are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.75,0:39:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我永遠無法擁有這樣一雙鞋.\NI'll never have shoes like those.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.81,0:39:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,來，穿上它們吧.\NHere, have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.10,0:39:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-給我？\N-是的.\N- For me?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.40,0:39:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}卡利托斯{\u0}！\NCarlitos!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.87,0:39:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}卡利托斯{\u0}！\NCarlitos!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.38,0:40:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-這是什麼？\N-{\u1}卡利托斯{\u0}的工具箱\N- What's this?\N- Carlitos' box.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.80,0:40:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你的鞋呢？\NWhere are your shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.26,0:40:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它們給了他.\NI gave them to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.85,0:40:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是瘋了？\NAre you mad or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.35,0:40:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我為他感到難過，他太窮了！\NI felt sorry for him. He's poor!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.85,0:40:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,去把它們要回來.\NGo and get them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.02,0:40:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，他跑去海邊了.\NI can't. He went to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.56,0:40:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那個小鬼會來取他的工具箱的.\NThat brat will be back\Nto fetch his box.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.44,0:40:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,去廣場等他，把鞋要回來，\NGo to the square,\Nwait for him
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.82,0:40:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他敢不給你就揍他一頓！\Nand get them, even if you have to punch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.07,0:40:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，爸爸.\NYes, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.78,0:41:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子怎麼了，教授？\NWhat happened to the boy,\Nprofessor?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.22,0:41:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他在礁石上玩耍，\NHe went to play on the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.27,0:41:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,膠底鞋使他滑倒了.\NThe rubber soles made him slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.97,0:41:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他跌入了大海，這個蠢孩子就這麼淹死了.\NHe fell into the sea.\NAnd the silly boy drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.68,0:41:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}就這樣，我童年的玩伴，化作了海灘的標誌，\N{\i1}And so our school friend\Nbecame a seaside icon,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.17,0:41:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}永遠被囚禁在這座庇護所之中，\N{\i1}imprisoned forever\Nin that sanctuary,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.89,0:41:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}供人祭奠、祈福.\N{\i1}devoted to the granting\Nof miracles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.15,0:41:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧.\NGo on!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.08,0:42:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}苦難，救濟，\N{\i1}Suffering, relief,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.21,0:42:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}救濟，苦難...\N{\i1}relief, suffering...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.42,0:42:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}這鏈條永遠不會終結.\N{\i1}the chain is never-ending.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.09,0:42:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你們有一個小時自由玩耍！\NYou can play for an hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.35,0:42:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，{\u1}匹諾曹{\u0}.\NHey, Pinocchio!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.77,0:42:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-想跟我們一起玩兒嗎？\N-在哪裡？\N- Do you want to come with us?\N- Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.09,0:42:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊的岩石之間.\NAmong the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.97,0:42:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-我們準備打主教.\N-打什麼？\N- We're going to beat the bishop.\N- Beat the what?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.72,0:42:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,來了你就懂了.\NCome and find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.01,0:43:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,來啊，匹諾曹，來打倒他！你會喜歡的！\NCome on, Pinocchio, beat off!\NYou'll enjoy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.89,0:43:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他那根和別人不一樣，哈哈哈！\NHis prick is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.51,0:43:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都是香蕉，他是根蘑菇，哈哈哈！\NWe've got a banana,\Nhe's got a mushroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.91,0:43:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他沒有包皮，他的尖端是鈍的，哈哈哈.\NHe has no foreskin,\Nhis end is blunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.40,0:43:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你不合群，{\u1}匹諾曹{\u0}，走開吧.\NYour difference bothers us! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.86,0:43:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,醜陋的猶太人.\NUgly Jew!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.60,0:43:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}停步.\N{\i1}Stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.02,0:43:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\b0}別跳下去.\N{\i1}Don't jump!{\i0\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.57,0:44:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你不是孤獨的，有我陪著你.\N{\i1}You are not alone.\NYou are with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.49,0:44:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}所有你將要成為的，你已經成為了.\N{\i1}All you are going to be,\Nyou are already.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.08,0:44:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}所有你竭力尋求的，你已經得到了.\N{\i1}What you are looking for\Nis already within you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.41,0:44:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}擁抱你的苦難吧，\N{\i1}Embrace your sufferings,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.12,0:44:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}因為通過它們，你將來到我的身邊.\N{\i1}for through them\Nyou will reach me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.42,0:44:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}二十年后，我又會成為誰呢？\N{\i1}And who shall I be\Nin twenty years?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.26,0:44:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}一百年後，千萬年后呢？\N{\i1}In a hundred?\NIn tens of thousands?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.43,0:44:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}那時我的意識是否仍然需要一個肉體？\NWill my consciousness\Nstill need a body?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.14,0:44:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}對你而言，我尚不存在.\N{\i1}For you,\NI do not yet exist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.72,0:44:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}對我而言，你也已成泡影.\N{\i1}For me,\Nyou do not exist anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.31,0:44:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在時間的盡頭，\N{\i1}At the end of time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.15,0:44:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}當所有的物質，回歸到了原點，\N{\i1}when all matter returns\Nto its origin,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.53,0:44:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你和我，僅僅成為一段記憶，\N{\i1}you and I\Nwill have just been memories,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.36,0:44:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}沒有什麼是眞實的.\N{\i1}nothing real.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.70,0:44:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}某個東西在夢著我們.\N{\i1}Something is dreaming us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.24,0:44:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}擁抱這幻覺吧.\N{\i1}Embrace the illusion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.70,0:44:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}活下去.\N{\i1}Live!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.50,0:45:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,烏克蘭小屋！烏克蘭小屋！高價在我們這裡不值一提！\NCasa Ukrania!\NWe swallow high prices!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.38,0:45:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}傑{\u0}！\NJaime!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.90,0:45:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}亞歷桑德羅{\u0}！\NAlejandrito!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.65,0:45:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,下去，你這蠢貨！\NGet down, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.15,0:45:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是消防隊的一員，我也想參與滅火.\NI'm a fireman!\NI'm here to put out the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.99,0:45:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\u1}佩德拉薩{\u0}，關掉引擎！\N-不行.\N- Pedraza, stop the engine!\N- I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.12,0:45:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,貧民窟火勢正旺.\NThe slums are burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.78,0:45:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我們必須趕快，否則傷亡慘重！\NWe must hurry\Nor they'll be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.04,0:45:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡！抓緊了，你這白癡！\NDamn it!\NHold tight, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.23,0:46:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,拿好這個哨子.\NTake this whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.86,0:46:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這里的遊民都是竊賊.\NThese dossers are thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.44,0:46:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他們膽敢靠近，\NAs soon as they get too close,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.82,0:46:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你就吹響哨子，我會來趕走他們.\Nblow your whistle\Nand I'll kick them up the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.95,0:46:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了嗎？警覺！\NGot it? Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.89,0:46:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了，爸爸.\NGot it, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.31,0:46:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,走遠點！\NClear off!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.44,0:46:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,婊子養的！\NSon of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.56,0:46:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,滾開！\NFuck off!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.49,0:46:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這個，我沒有失職.\NHere. I didn't let them steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.03,0:46:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你在期許稱讚嗎？\NYou're looking for compliments?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.45,0:46:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是盡責而已.\NYou only did your duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.75,0:47:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,立定！\NHalt!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.84,0:47:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}佩德拉薩{\u0}長官哪兒去了！？\NCaptain Pedraza is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.88,0:47:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他還在那邊！\NHe's still over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.06,0:47:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在這兒！\NHere he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.69,0:47:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你看.\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.82,0:47:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看！\NLook!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.73,0:48:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,立定！\NHalt!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.76,0:48:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,神并不存在.\NGod does not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.34,0:48:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你會死去然後腐爛.\NYou die and you rot.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.01,0:48:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不存在超越於此的事物！\NThere's nothing beyond!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.36,0:48:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我死了，爸爸.\NI'm dead, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.79,0:48:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜，你這寄生蟲.\NCalm down, you louse!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.98,0:48:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,別讓我難堪.\NDon't embarrass me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.82,0:48:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我們的吉祥物！\NYou're the mascot!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.83,0:49:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事.\NIt's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.88,0:49:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他很好.\NHe'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.88,0:49:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是有點發熱.\NHe woke up with a temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.63,0:49:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我會送他回家，隨後就歸隊.\NI'll take him home and come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.72,0:49:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續進行！\NCarry on!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.40,0:49:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒叫醒我，已經這麼晚了.\NYou didn't wake me up!\NIt's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.86,0:49:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我上學遲到了.\NI've missed school.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.52,0:49:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你在葬禮上昏倒了.\NYou fainted at the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.08,0:49:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,醫生說你需要休息.\NThe doctor said to let you rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.87,0:49:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你睡了整整兩天.\NYou slept solidly for two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.60,0:49:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺好些了嗎？\NDo you feel better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.32,0:49:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，爸爸，我挺好的.\NYes, Papa, I feel really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.08,0:49:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是麼，我感覺很糟.\NWell, I feel really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.96,0:49:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你表現得像個懦夫.\NYou acted like a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.51,0:49:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,現在，他們都在恥笑我.\NNow they're laughing at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.93,0:50:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果兒子是懦夫，那父親肯定也一樣.\NIf the son is a coward,\Nthe father must be too.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.14,0:50:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就算身穿消防員的裝束，猶太人不過是猶太人.\NEven dressed up as a fireman,\Na Jew is a Jew.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.48,0:50:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-我很抱歉，爸爸.\N-閉嘴！\N- I'm very sorry, Papa.\N- Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.38,0:50:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,看著它.\NLook!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.43,0:50:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,市長先生，他們來了.\NMr Mayor, they're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.43,0:50:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-多少人？\N-三百人.\N- How many?\N- 300.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.94,0:50:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.79,0:51:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快點，{\u1}奎瓦斯{\u0}，\NHurry, Cuevas,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.50,0:51:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,拉響警笛！\Ngive the alarm!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.95,0:52:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,停下腳步！\NNow stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.62,0:52:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,膽敢往前一公分，\NIf you dare move an inch,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.03,0:52:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就射穿你！\Nwe'll shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.95,0:52:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你們對{\u1}托科皮亞{\u0}是一個威脅.\NYou pose a threat to all of Tocopilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.08,0:52:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你們攜帶著鼠疫！\NYou're carrying the plague!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.13,0:52:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有水嗎？哪裡能喝到水？\NWhat about water? Where's the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.28,0:52:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,問神去要吧！\NAsk God for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.49,0:52:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,給我們水，該死的！\NWater, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.60,0:52:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,水！\NWater!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.64,0:52:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要水！\NWe want water!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.64,0:52:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,水！\NWater!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.89,0:52:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,肅靜！\NSilence!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.68,0:52:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,若不保持肅靜，\NIf you don't keep quiet,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.48,0:52:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就把你們全部射死！\Nyou'll all be shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.53,0:53:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,全部！\NAll of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.69,0:53:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，{\u1}傑{\u0}！\NWait, Jaime!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.20,0:53:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這太瘋狂了！不要去！\NIt's crazy! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.74,0:53:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜點，女人！\NSilence, woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.33,0:53:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我會讓那群該死的消防員看看，\NI will show those fucking firemen
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.04,0:53:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,到底誰更勇敢！\NI'm braver than them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.05,0:53:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,水！\NWater!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.55,0:53:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,水！\NWater!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.97,0:53:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,鎮靜，所有人都有份！\NCalm down,\Nthere's enough for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.64,0:53:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我的驢子！\NMy donkeys!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.18,0:54:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.35,0:54:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.93,0:54:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你們在吃我的驢子！\NYou're eating my donkeys!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.60,0:54:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我明天要如何再送水來？\NHow will I bring the water tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.36,0:54:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,明天？我們今天還沒吃飽！\NTomorrow? We're hungry today!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.82,0:55:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}傑{\u0}！\NJaime!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.41,0:55:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸！\NPapa!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.43,0:55:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他們會來燒了我！\NThey're going to burn me!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.30,0:55:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸！\NPapa!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.62,0:55:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不會的！\NNever!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.46,0:55:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他們永遠別想燒了你！\NThey will never burn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.59,0:55:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了，別把你自己鎖在裡面！\NThat's enough,\Ndon't shut yourself in!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.26,0:55:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不屈服，你們全家都要受死.\NIf you don't surrender,\Nyou will all die.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.85,0:55:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你的商店，會成為傳染源！\NYour shop will be\Na source of infection!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.02,0:55:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我親愛的兒子，\NMy dear son,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.40,0:55:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你絕不能被感染.\Nyou mustn't get infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.40,0:55:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧，去洗凈你的雙手，\NGo and wash your hands
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.65,0:55:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,躲在浴室中吧.\Nand lock yourself in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.53,0:55:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，媽媽.\NYes, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.19,0:56:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,神啊，\NGod,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.69,0:56:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我感覺得到你就在我體內.\NI feel You inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.53,0:56:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你的一部分.\NI am a part of You.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.63,0:56:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不值一提，\NI am nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.38,0:56:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我愚昧無知，\NI know nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.18,0:57:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我渺小無力.\NI can do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.56,0:57:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你是萬事萬物，\NYou are everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.69,0:57:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你洞悉一切，\NYou know everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.99,0:57:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你全知全能！\NYou can do everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.29,0:57:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我是淺灘，\NI am the bank
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.00,0:57:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,而你，\Nof the vast river
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.09,0:57:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是廣闊的河川.\Nthat You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.39,0:57:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,從我身上奔湧而過，\NBreak through me
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.10,0:57:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,以你那治愈的洪濤中\Nand let the waters
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.19,0:57:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,湧動的水流\Nof Your healing flood
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.45,0:58:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,沖洗他吧！\Nwash over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.29,0:59:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}傑{\u0}.\NJaime.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.21,0:59:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這是個奇跡！\NIt's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.21,0:59:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，不，不，我救不了人們.\NNo, no!\NI couldn't save the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.17,0:59:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡沒有我的根.\NI have no roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.13,0:59:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡不是我的祖國.\NThis is not my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.30,0:59:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我輸了.\NI failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.39,0:59:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能輸.\NYou cannot fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.43,0:59:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你同斯大林一樣強大.\NYou are as strong as Stalin.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.88,0:59:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.69,1:00:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，你是.\NYes, you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.36,1:00:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至更強.\NEven stronger.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.66,1:00:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你同神一樣強大.\NYou are as strong as God.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.66,1:00:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,神不存在！\NGod does not exist!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.70,1:00:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他存在.\NYes He does.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.83,1:00:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是他治愈了你.\NHe cured you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.17,1:00:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在你心中\NFeel His presence
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.97,1:00:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,感知此時此地的他吧.\Nin your heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.07,1:00:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的心中，只有你.\NIn my heart,\Nthere is only you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.99,1:00:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}薩若{\u0}，\NSara,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.45,1:00:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}薩若{\u0}，{\u1}薩若{\u0}，\NSara, Sara,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.20,1:00:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的{\u1}薩若{\u0}，\Nmy Sara,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.83,1:01:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我摯愛的{\u1}薩若{\u0}，\Nmy devoted Sara,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.54,1:01:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我飽受苦難的{\u1}薩若{\u0}，請原諒我.\Nmy long-suffering Sara,\Nforgive me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.13,1:01:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你喚回了我的力量.\NYou have restored my strength.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.05,1:01:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如今我知道該怎樣拯救所有窮人了！\NNow I know how to save all the poor!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.35,1:01:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}智利{\u0}不能永遠被暴君編織的謊言蒙蔽.\NChile cannot put up\Nwith a tyrant's lies forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.61,1:01:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我要前往{\u1}聖地亞哥{\u0}，\NI'll go to Santiago
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.52,1:01:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,為他的腦袋放入一枚子彈！\Nand put a bullet through his head!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.20,1:01:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,玩兒夠了吧！我們沒時間奉陪！\NEnough now!\NWe won't wait any longer!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.87,1:01:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻出來，否則我燒了你的店鋪！\NCome out right away,\Nor we'll burn your shop!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.46,1:01:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他們屈服了.\NThey're surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.67,1:01:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我們很健康，同志們.\NWe are alive, comrades.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.89,1:01:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\u1}伊瓦涅斯{\u0}去死吧！\N-去死！\N- Death to Ibáñez!\N- Death!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.28,1:02:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,看看這個，同志！\NHere it is, comrades!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.49,1:02:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哈利路亞，我找到了！\NHallelujah, I found it!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.62,1:02:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-不，是我找的！\N-閉嘴，同志.\N- No, I did!\N- Shut up, comrade.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.29,1:02:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-閉嘴，同志！\NShut up, comrade!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.91,1:02:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我不閉.\NI won't shut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.92,1:02:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,利己主義者！\NIndividualist!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.96,1:02:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,算了.\NI'll shut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.01,1:02:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,睡吧，\NGo to sleep,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.51,1:02:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我的甜心.\Nmy little sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.27,1:02:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}薩若{\u0}.\NSara!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.69,1:02:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,看！\NLook!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.65,1:02:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到他的弱點了.\NI found his weak spot.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.95,1:02:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他愛自己養的馬勝過了一切！\NHe loves his horse more than anything else！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.67,1:03:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人會搜我這裡.\NNo bloody soldier will search me here.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.14,1:03:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}傑{\u0}，你瘋了！\NJaime, you're mad!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.66,1:03:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我失敗了，\NIf I fail,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.49,1:03:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也許再也見不到彼此.\Nwe may never see one another again.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.90,1:04:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我活著一日，\NAs long as I live,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.49,1:04:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就愛你一日.\NI will love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.66,1:04:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我存在於世，\NAs long as I live,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.04,1:04:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就愛你永遠.\NI will love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.09,1:04:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但這愛多麼孤單,\NBut this love so lonely
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.19,1:04:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,蘊我胸口,\Nin my breast
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.32,1:04:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,它將找到一個庇護所，\Nwill find sanctuary
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.28,1:05:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,成為屬於我自己的\Nand be a secret
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.16,1:05:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一個秘密.\Nof my own.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.96,1:05:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,成為屬於我自己的\NAnd be a secret
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.13,1:05:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一個秘密.\Nof my own.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.85,1:05:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我活著一日，\NAs long as I live,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.98,1:05:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就愛你一日.\NI will love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.15,1:05:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽！\NMama!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.24,1:05:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我.\NForgive me!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.38,1:06:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,起來，饑寒交迫的奴隸，\NArise ye workers from your slumbers
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.89,1:06:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你想殺掉{\u1}伊瓦涅斯{\u0}.\NYou want to kill Ibáñez.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.98,1:06:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是秘密警察嗎？\NAre you the secret police?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.23,1:06:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-你要逮捕我嗎？\N-並非如此.\N- Are you arresting me?\N- It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.82,1:06:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓你得逞因為這件事必須我來做！\NI won't let you kill him\Nbecause I have to do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.78,1:06:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,三個理由：第一，你是個猶太佬，\NFor three reasons: One, you are a Jew
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.87,1:06:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,必須由智利人處決他.\Nand a Chilean must kill him.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.16,1:06:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,第二，\NTwo,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.46,1:06:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你老了而我很年輕.\Nyou are old and I am young.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.29,1:06:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,第三，那個處決他的人，將留名青史.\NThree, he who kills him will go down in history.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.80,1:06:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,而那一定會是我！\NAnd that has to be me!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.13,1:06:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,放手！\NLet go!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.51,1:06:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你這白癡！\NYou idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.14,1:06:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-哪裡來的槍？\N-是我父親的，\N- Where did you get this gun?\N- It was my father's,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.64,1:06:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一名批判{\u1}伊瓦涅斯{\u0}的記者.\Na journalist who criticised Ibáñez.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.73,1:06:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他們逮捕并殺害了他.\NThey arrested and killed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.28,1:06:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白.\NNow I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.69,1:07:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你並非想留名青史，你想替父親報仇.\NYou don't want to go down in history,\Nyou want to avenge your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.70,1:07:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,為除掉他我願奉獻我的生命.\NI'll give my life to get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.83,1:07:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧.\NAlright.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.70,1:07:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣，\NLook,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.87,1:07:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,毀了他的世界吧，你來，\Nyou rid the world of him
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.04,1:07:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我協助.\Nand I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.75,1:07:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,行吧，同志.\NAlright, comrade.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.73,1:07:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,女士們先生們，心愛小狗的主人們，\NLadies and gentlemen,\Nowners of these beloved dogs,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.15,1:07:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,現在是頒獎時間.\Nthe time has come to award our two prizes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.82,1:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,第一個獎項，\NFirst prize,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.49,1:07:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,金骨頭，\Nthe Golden Bone,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.24,1:07:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,得主是，蝴蝶犬.\Ngoes to the butterfly-dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.29,1:07:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊，請.\NThis way, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.38,1:08:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,銀骨頭，\NAnd the Lead Bone,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.97,1:08:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,頒給最蠢著裝，\Nfor the worst costume,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.72,1:08:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,得主是...\Ngoes...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.43,1:08:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,袋鼠犬.\Nto the kangaroo-dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.79,1:08:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,肅靜！奏樂！奏國歌！\NSilence! Music!\NThe national anthem!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.45,1:09:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,別開槍！\NDon't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.75,1:09:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他不至於得到這樣一種死！\NHe doesn't deserve\Nsuch a death!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.33,1:09:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,死就是死.\NDeath is death!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.80,1:09:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想生活在一個有著喬裝打扮的狗的世界.\NI don't want to live in a world\Nof dressed up dogs.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.81,1:09:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,它讓我惡心.\NIt makes me sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.15,1:09:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,異教徒！你毀了我的基督！\NHeretics!\NYou destroyed my Christ!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.28,1:09:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,立定！\NHalt!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.33,1:10:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,別瞄準這個男人.\NDon't shoot this man!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.80,1:10:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,把這個可憐人送去公墓,\NTake this poor man\Nto the communal grave,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.55,1:10:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,和他的袋鼠犬一起.\Ntogether with his kangaroo-dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.30,1:10:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,演出必須繼續進行！\NThe show must go on!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.51,1:10:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,為了救總統，\NTo save the President,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.06,1:10:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這個男人冒著生命的危險！\Nthis man risked his life!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.15,1:10:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果槍點火了，你現在已成死尸.\NIf the gun had fired,\Nyou would be dead now.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.57,1:10:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你應當得到回報.\NYou deserve a reward.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.91,1:10:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是要錢，先生，\NI'm not asking for money, sir,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.70,1:10:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這只是我的善意.\Njust a favour.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.00,1:10:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我很愛馬，\NAs I love horses,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.58,1:10:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我夢想能成為你的馬夫.\Nmy dream would be to become your groom.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.76,1:10:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你的請求適時.\NYour request is timely.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.43,1:10:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}阿基里斯{\u0}先生，我的老馬夫，\NDon Aquiles,\Nmy old groom,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.30,1:10:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,想要退休了.\Nwants to retire.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.68,1:11:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我會送你去我的宅子，那裡他可以訓練你.\NI'll send you to my estate so he can train you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.81,1:11:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一到兩個月時間，我們到時看看你進展如何.\NIn a month or two, I'll see how you're getting on.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.93,1:11:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}阿基里斯{\u0}為您效勞，先生.\NAquiles, at your service, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.39,1:11:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不必太過恭敬，{\u1}阿基里斯{\u0}先生.\NNo need to be so respectful,\NDon Aquiles.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.86,1:11:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我僅僅是你的學生.\NI am merely your pupil.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.03,1:11:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來.\NCome along with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.16,1:11:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這塊地上唯一的建築，\NThe only buildings on the land
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.53,1:12:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這些皇家馬廄，\Nare these right royal stables,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.87,1:12:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,只為{\u1}布塞弗勒斯{\u0}而造，我的國王.\Nmade just for Bucephalus, my king.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.08,1:12:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我來向你介紹我的美人.\NI'll introduce you\Nto my handsome.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.42,1:12:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但要千萬小心，他不太信任人.\NBut be right careful,\Nhe don't trust nobody.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.76,1:12:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你睡這裡,\NYou'll be sleeping here,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.05,1:12:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就在我旁邊.\Nright next to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.93,1:12:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要在每天破曉時分準時起床，\NFor we'll be up\Nat the crack of dawn every day
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.02,1:12:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,來檢查{\u1}布塞弗勒斯{\u0}的健康和情緒.\Nto see to Bucephalus'\Nhealth and comfort.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.36,1:12:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,跑吧.\NWalk!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.92,1:12:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他聊聊.\NTalk to him now.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.51,1:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你的聲音必須直抵它的耳蝸，進入它的心靈.\NYour voice must go right in his ear\Nto reach his heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.30,1:13:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\u1}布塞弗勒斯{\u0}.\N-那聲音來自你的腦殼.\N - Bucephalus.\N- That voice is from your head!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.14,1:13:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,認真點兒，夥計！\NC'mon, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.56,1:13:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,試著理解.\NTry to understand that.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.68,1:13:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,它應當發自你胸口，\NIt's got to be from your chest.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.31,1:13:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,由內心深處.\NRight from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.03,1:13:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}布塞弗勒斯{\u0}...\NBucephalus...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.83,1:13:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你擁有一切.\Nyou have everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.67,1:13:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我在街頭長大，\NI grew up on the streets,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.21,1:13:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,飽受蔑視，\Ntreated with contempt,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.00,1:13:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,遊走于殘酷的人群中，\Namongst cruel people,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.30,1:13:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,像狗一樣咆哮，\Nhowling like a dog
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.97,1:13:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,只為了一點感情.\Nfor a bit of affection.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.14,1:13:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他們把我鎖進了一個堡壘.\NThey shut me up in a fortress.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.89,1:13:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我成了這樣，\NAnd there I remain,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.02,1:13:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,對感情感到飢餓.\Nhungry for affection.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.82,1:13:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人給過我現在你給我的感覺.\NNo one has given me\Nwhat you give me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.95,1:14:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好，{\u1}傑{\u0}！\NWell done, Jaime!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.92,1:14:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你就要贏得{\u1}布塞弗勒斯{\u0}的芳心了.\NYou'll win over Bucephalus yet!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.25,1:14:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,眞是非常好！\NReally well done!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.71,1:14:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你可以帶他走走了.\NNow you can take him for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.66,1:14:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了，先生？\NYes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.66,1:14:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我願為您效勞，{\u1}卡洛斯{\u0}閣下.\NI'm at your service, Don Carlos.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.17,1:14:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}布塞弗勒斯{\u0}很不錯.\NBucephalus is right well.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.59,1:14:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是，先生.\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.17,1:14:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是，他會被備好的.\NYes, he'll be saddled up.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.67,1:15:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.38,1:15:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,上校隨時會要求\NThe colonel can ask at any time
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.06,1:15:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,來看望他的摯友.\Nafter his best friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.85,1:15:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他明天就要來.\NHe's coming tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.89,1:15:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,對我來說，是時候該走了.\NAs for me, the time has come to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.44,1:15:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.36,1:15:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你的墳鑿好了，阿基里斯先生.\NHere is your grave,\NDon Aquiles.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.67,1:15:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,脫下你的衣服，\NTake off your clothes
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.42,1:15:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,穿上我的.\Nand put on mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.56,1:15:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,永遠別摘下這頂帽子，朋友.\NNever take this hat off, friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.40,1:16:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣{\u1}布塞弗勒斯{\u0}就永遠不會知道我走了.\NThat way Bucephalus\Nwill never know I've gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.69,1:16:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定會像愛我般愛你.\NFor sure he'll love you\Nas much as me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.70,1:16:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我要放下我的靈魂了，\NI'm giving up my soul,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.20,1:16:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,它想要回家，\Nit wants to return home.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.92,1:16:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,它只是偶然經過，遇到我.\NIt was just passing through here\Nwith me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.63,1:16:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,多往我身上蓋點土.\NThrow plenty of earth on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.09,1:16:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,保證我被完全掩埋.\NMake sure I'm well covered.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.26,1:16:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,明天，什麼都不要告訴總統.\NTomorrow, don't say anything\Nto the President.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.52,1:16:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他不會注意到我走了.\NHe won't even notice I left.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.90,1:16:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,結果，當權者要考慮太多問題，\NAfter all, the mighty\Nhave too much on their minds
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.40,1:16:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,根本無法記住我這樣的老鬼.\Nto remember an old bloke like me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.74,1:16:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你，{\u1}傑{\u0}，我的朋友.\NThank you, Jaime, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.57,1:18:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊，{\u1}阿基里斯{\u0}先生.\NHello, Don Aquiles.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.32,1:18:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\u1}布塞弗勒斯{\u0}還好嗎？\N-他很好，先生.\N- How is Bucephalus?\N- Very well, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.41,1:18:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可我不是{\u1}阿基里斯{\u0}.\NBut I am not Aquiles.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.87,1:18:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,狗類大賽，先生...\NThe dog competition, sir...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.79,1:18:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，對了！我怎能把你忘了？\NAh, yes!\NHow could I forget you?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.80,1:18:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事了.\NIt's fine!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.80,1:18:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,等在這兒.\NWait here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.10,1:18:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}布塞弗勒斯{\u0}，\NBucephalus,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.10,1:18:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我親愛的.\Nmy love.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.35,1:18:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你長得多英俊，我的王子.\NYou look so handsome, my prince.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.94,1:18:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們看看你.\NLet's have a look at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.36,1:18:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,很好.\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.95,1:18:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很好.\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.66,1:18:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,閃耀，閃耀，多麼美啊！\NSplendid, splendid.\NWhat a beauty!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.54,1:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜你，{\u1}阿基里斯{\u0}先生，\NCongratulations, Don Aquiles,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.71,1:19:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我的馬從未像現在看上去這麼優秀.\Nmy horse has never\Nlooked so well.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.63,1:19:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,給你.\NHere you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.26,1:19:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想要錢，先生.\NI don't want money, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.42,1:19:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-這都是愛的功勞.\N-我欣賞你的態度.\N- It's a labour of love.\N- I like your attitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.93,1:19:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,給你的供給加倍！\NI'll double your supplies!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.81,1:19:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,起身，阿基里斯，我們不是在教堂.\NGet up, Aquiles!\NWe're not in church.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.86,1:19:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我準備先小跑一下，然後奔馳一小時.\NI'm going to trot\Nthen gallop for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.03,1:19:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來後，會把他交給你.\NWhen I come back,\NI'll leave the animal with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.24,1:19:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你要供他水和食物.\NYou will give him water and food.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.71,1:19:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我的馬是神聖的.\NFor my horse is sacred.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.17,1:19:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舞吧.\NDance!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.89,1:20:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，{\u1}布塞弗勒斯{\u0}！\NAh, Bucephalus!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.78,1:20:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他的罪行並非源於邪惡的靈魂，\NHis crimes are not the result of a wicked soul,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.96,1:20:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,而是源於他磅礴的志氣.\Nbut of an overwhelming generosity.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.25,1:20:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了！\NEnough!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.38,1:20:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,讓這些詭辯在我腦中消失！\NOut of my head\Ntreacherous thoughts!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.84,1:20:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是一個好父親，\NHe is not a good father,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.80,1:20:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他是頭惹人厭的豬，\Nhe's a disgusting pig,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.84,1:20:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,一頭嗜血的畜生，\Na bloodthirsty brute,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.97,1:20:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一個癡癲的極端利己主義者！\Na cretinous egomaniac!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.06,1:20:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他是個渾身屎臭的該死的軍人！\NHe's a damn soldier full of shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.99,1:21:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,留心黃色的花朵.\NBe careful with the yellow flowers!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.16,1:21:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,馬兒們瘋狂地喜歡它.\NThese horses are wild about them.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.58,1:21:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而它卻是一劑致死的毒藥.\NBut it's a deadly poison.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.39,1:21:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡它們，是嗎？\NYou like them, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.35,1:21:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧.\NEat.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.83,1:21:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,主人，主人！\NMaster, master!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.37,1:21:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了什麼！？\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.92,1:21:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我，阿基里斯！\N它怎麼了！？\NAnswer, Aquiles!\NWhat happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.17,1:21:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,神怎能允許這種事發生？\NHow can God allow this?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.63,1:21:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼高貴的一頭野獸！\NSuch a noble beast!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.09,1:22:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,放鬆點，放鬆.\NEasy now, easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.01,1:22:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是要給你打一針，\NI'll just give you an injection
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.93,1:22:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你會好起來的.\Nand you'll feel better.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.48,1:22:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,乖孩子.\NThat's my boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.15,1:22:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,該死的神，我要殺了你！\NDamn God, I'm going to shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.02,1:22:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你馬上就會好起來.\NYou're going to feel better.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.99,1:22:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}布塞弗勒斯{\u0}！\NBucephalus!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.21,1:22:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,求你不要死！\NPlease don't die!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.00,1:22:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,求你不要死！\NPlease don't die!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.47,1:22:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！\NDon't die!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.22,1:23:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你！\NThank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.83,1:23:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要把這裡燒掉.\NWe're going to burn it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.00,1:23:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,全燒掉.\NAll of it!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.10,1:24:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直是一位忠實的僕人.\NYou have always been\Na most loyal servant.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.52,1:24:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這次，收下這些錢吧.\NThis time, take the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.40,1:24:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,全收下，\NKeep it all
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.90,1:24:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,離開這裡吧.\Nand go away.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.02,1:24:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有了.\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.15,1:24:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有了.\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.66,1:25:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽！\NMama!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.54,1:25:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了，{\u1}亞歷桑德羅{\u0}？\NWhat's the matter,\NAlejandrito?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.75,1:25:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在水泥鑄造的搖籃里，\N{\i1}Being in a cradle of cement,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.34,1:25:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}被一片龐大的陰影繈褓著，\N{\i1}swaddled in a gigantic shadow,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.14,1:25:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}束縛於自身虛無的存在.\N{\i1}bound to my empty existence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.14,1:25:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}困陷在這座肉體的島嶼上，\N{\i1}Trapped in this island of flesh,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.31,1:25:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}通過記憶尋找自我，\N{\i1}searching for myself in memories,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.15,1:25:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}什麼人也沒找到.\N{\i1}and meeting no one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.40,1:25:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗，正在吞噬一切.\NThe darkness\Nis swallowing everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.03,1:25:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,它會毀滅我們.\NIt's going to devour us.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.99,1:25:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}亞歷桑德羅{\u0}，\NAlejandrito,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.24,1:25:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛你對嗎？\Ndo I love you?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.20,1:25:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，媽媽.\NYes, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.62,1:25:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有多愛？\NHow much?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.25,1:26:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,像從天空到大地那樣寬廣.\NFrom the sky to the earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.04,1:26:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是我的愛，\NThis is not my love,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.84,1:26:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這是來自神的愛，\Nit comes from God,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.26,1:26:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我僅僅是個信使.\NI am merely the sender.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.14,1:26:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,正是神創造了一切，\NAs God creates all,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.51,1:26:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我們都在傳播他的愛.\Nso we all radiate His love.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.36,1:26:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我的兒子，\NMy son,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.40,1:26:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗其實像我一樣深愛著你，\Nthe darkness loves you\Nas much as I do,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.70,1:26:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因為它是神的影子.\Nfor it is God's shadow.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.95,1:26:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很害怕.\NI'm really scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.96,1:26:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,它會消失的.\NIt's going to vanish.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.20,1:27:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,黑色，\NBlack,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.20,1:27:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,黑色，黑色.\Nblack, black.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.60,1:27:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你和它一樣了，\NNow you're just the same,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.02,1:27:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你屬於黑暗.\Nyou belong to the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.06,1:27:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗是你的王國，\NDarkness is your kingdom
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.02,1:27:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你是夜晚的怪物.\Nand you are a monster\Nof the night.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.95,1:27:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你非常飢餓.\NYou are hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.99,1:27:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我很飢餓！\NI am hungry!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.32,1:28:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要吞掉一位公主，來哺饗你的飢餓，\NTo feed your hunger\Nyou need to devour a princess,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.79,1:28:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,雪白無比的公主.\Never so white.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.54,1:28:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,雪白無比！\NEver so white!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.51,1:28:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,公主躲了起來.\NThe princess hides.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.51,1:28:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怪物要抓住她.\NThe monster has to catch her.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.14,1:28:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,數到十！\NCount up to ten!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.14,1:28:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一，\NOne,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.23,1:28:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,二，三，四，五，\Ntwo, three, four, five,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.90,1:28:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,六，七，八，九，十！\Nsix, seven, eight, nine, ten!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.86,1:28:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我來了！\NHere I come!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.34,1:28:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,黑色.\NBlack.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.50,1:28:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,黑色.\NBlack.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.80,1:28:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,黑色.\NBlack.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.56,1:29:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我的母親溶入了黑暗.\N{\i1}My mother dissolved\Ninto the darkness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.85,1:29:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}從此我再也不恐懼夜晚.\N{\i1}And never again\Nwas I scared of the night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.49,1:29:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}卡利托斯{\u0}？\NCarlitos?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.78,1:29:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能！你是鬼魂嗎？\NIt can't be!\NAre you a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.91,1:29:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你這白癡，我是他孿生兄弟{\u1}盧喬{\u0}.\NYou idiot,\NI'm his twin Lucho!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.33,1:29:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-我很愛他.\N-放開我！\N- I loved him.\N- Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.67,1:29:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是你殺了他.\NYou killed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.54,1:29:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,從我視線中消失！我要工作了！\NOut of my sight!\NLet me work!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.09,1:30:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,小{\u1}盧喬{\u0}！\NLuchito!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.51,1:30:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜！\NQuiet!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.47,1:30:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,快看看誰在這兒！\NJust look at what we have here!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.73,1:30:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰屈尊來探望我們？\NWho deigns to visit us?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.56,1:30:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一個渾身肥皂臭的富家子弟！\NA rich boy stinking of soap!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.23,1:30:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這個黑小子是我們的冠軍.\NThis dark one\Nis our champion.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.19,1:30:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們看看這個蒼白的小子能不能保護自己！\NLet's see if Paleface\Ncan defend himself!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.11,1:30:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,下注吧！\NPlace your bets!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.24,1:30:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,富人還是窮人？\NThe rich or the poor?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.37,1:30:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,窮人！\NThe poor one!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.49,1:30:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,散開點兒！\NMake a space!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.58,1:30:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,出拳吧！誰先哭出來誰就輸了.\NLet the punches fly!\NThe first who cries loses.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.46,1:30:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-他是我的朋友！\N-我才不是，你這個蹩腳的猶太人.\N- He's my friend!\N- No, I'm not, you crappy Jew.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.67,1:30:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,預備！\NGet ready!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.96,1:30:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-一.\N-一！\N- One.\N- One!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.51,1:31:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-二.\N-二！\N- Two.\N- Two!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.80,1:31:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-三.\N-三！\N- Three.\N- Three!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.56,1:31:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這不能算！他從後方偷襲！\NThat doesn't count! He came from behind!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.48,1:31:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不能算！\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.10,1:31:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜！\NQuiet!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.60,1:31:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,快來，他任你處置！痛毆這個叛徒！\NCome on, he's all yours! Hit that traitor!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.36,1:31:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了？\NWhat have you done?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.74,1:31:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事.我遇到了點意外.\NNothing. I was in La Urgencia.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.37,1:31:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他們笑我是猶太人，還打了我.\NThey called me a Jew\Nand hit me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.66,1:31:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想適應環境，\NIf you want to survive
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.83,1:31:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你就要和光同塵.\Nyou must go unnoticed.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.13,1:31:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我會將這些障礙從你腦子里去除.\NI'm going to remove\Nthese barriers from your mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.14,1:31:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,丟掉{\u1}匹諾曹{\u0}！\NOut with Pinocchio!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.94,1:31:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,丟掉猶太人！\NOut with the Jew!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.40,1:31:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,丟掉鼻子和白皮膚！\NOut with the nose\Nand white skin!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.82,1:32:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你完全空了！\NYou are empty!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.12,1:32:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你成為了不可見的！\NYou are invisible!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.54,1:32:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你確定沒人能看見我？\NAre you sure I am invisible?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.25,1:32:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,來.\NCome!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.47,1:32:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我會脫光衣服，\NI will get undressed
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.80,1:32:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,走進裡面去.\Nand go inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.64,1:32:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,別，媽媽，這太危險了！\NNo, Mama, it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.85,1:32:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,相信吧.\NHave faith!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.20,1:33:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}亞歷桑德羅{\u0}.\NAlejandrito!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.93,1:33:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就像空氣.\NWe are like air.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.81,1:34:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他們看不見我們，{\u1}亞歷桑德羅{\u0}，\NThey do not see us, Alejandrito,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.73,1:34:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,更聽不見我們.\Nnor do they hear us.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.32,1:34:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,空氣...\NAir...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.16,1:34:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就是空氣.\NWe are air.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.71,1:34:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你教給爸爸如何隱形了嗎？\NDid you teach my father to be invisible?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.22,1:34:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他不相信這些事.\NHe doesn't believe in such things.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.80,1:34:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以死亡看得見他啊.\NThen Death can see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.72,1:34:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,也許它已經把他帶走了.\NMaybe it has taken him away.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.77,1:34:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不，他沒死.\NNo, he's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.98,1:34:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他死了，\NIf he was
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.40,1:34:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我心中一定會感知到.\Nmy heart would tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.65,1:34:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那他在哪裡？\NWhere is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.71,1:35:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這塊岩石\NThis stone
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.08,1:35:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,知道{\u1}傑{\u0}在哪裡.\Nknows where Jaime is.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.75,1:35:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你要傳達給他你的消息.\NYou are going to send him a message.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.26,1:35:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,唾在上面.\NSpit.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.06,1:35:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴他你想說的話語.\NNow tell him\Nwhat it is you want to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.23,1:35:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,別忘記我們，回來吧.\NDon't forget us.\NCome back.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.37,1:37:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,停下！走遠點！\NStop it! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.96,1:37:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}楚蔻{\u0}，我漂亮的小狗.\NCuco, my pretty dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.92,1:37:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎麼了？\N-女士，我的名字不叫{\u1}楚蔻{\u0}.\N- What's the matter?\N- Madam, my name isn't Cuco.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.05,1:37:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫{\u1}傑·佐杜洛夫斯基{\u0}！\NI am Jaime Jodorowsky!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.27,1:37:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我為什麼在這裡？\NWhat am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.35,1:37:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼說你恢復了記憶.\NSo your memory has returned.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.15,1:37:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,夢結束了.\NThe dream is over.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.65,1:37:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.61,1:37:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來.\NGet up.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.07,1:37:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我發現你時你正流落街頭，\NI found you wandering the streets,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.70,1:37:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,飢腸轆轆.\Nhalf starved.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.29,1:37:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,終於，殘酷的神派來了一位不討厭我的人.\NFinally, cruel God sent someone\Nwho wasn't repulsed by me.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.04,1:37:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我把你帶來和我一起生活.\NI brought you to live with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.09,1:37:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜到總有一天你會記起你是誰，\NSuspecting you would one day\Nbe yourself again,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.05,1:37:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我給你寫了一封信.\NI wrote you a letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.89,1:38:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人能逃離自己的命運.\NNo one escapes from their destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.31,1:38:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我讀了它你就全明白了.\NI'll read it so you understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.23,1:38:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,“遇見你，就像找到一件珍寶.\N"Meeting you was like finding treasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.45,1:38:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我就像一隻野狗，\N"I was like a street dog,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.36,1:38:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,在垃圾堆里翻到什麼吃什麼，\N"eating what I could find\Nin the rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.70,1:38:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人給我一分錢.\N"Nobody gave me a cent.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.91,1:38:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我在你手臂上塗了我們國旗的顏色，\N"I painted your arms\Nthe colours of our flag,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.04,1:38:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你癱瘓的手\N"and your paralysed hands
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.84,1:38:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,成為了窮苦人民的標誌.\N"became a symbol of the people's misery.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.92,1:38:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,白天，你是我的寄託，\N"In the day, you were my sustenance,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.01,1:38:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,夜晚，你是我的榮光.\N"and at night, my glory.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.72,1:38:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,儘管你無法在床笫間\N"Even though you couldn't caress me,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.64,1:38:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,愛撫我，\N"in bed on your back,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.85,1:38:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我也可以騎在你身上.\N"I would mount you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.73,1:38:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你總有一天會醒來，\N"Knowing you would wake up\None day,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.23,1:38:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的相聚讓我感到愉悅，\N"I felt the joy of our union
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.74,1:39:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,也帶來了心知定會別離的痛苦.\N"and the pain of knowing\Nit wouldn't last.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.57,1:39:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,找回你的記憶，\N"Recovering your memory,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.95,1:39:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你就從我生命中消失了，\N"you disappear from my life
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.74,1:39:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因此我的生命也消失了.”\N"and therefore\Nmy life disappears."
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.96,1:39:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我的愛人，\NMy love,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.50,1:39:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,願殘酷的神治愈你這雙手.\Nmay cruel God heal these hands of yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.13,1:39:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,它們是我渺小存在中的珠寶.\NThey have been the jewels\Nof my poor existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.06,1:40:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,找回你的記憶，\NRecovering your memory,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.64,1:40:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你就從我生命中消失了，\Nyou disappear from my life
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.65,1:40:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因此我的生命也消失了.\Nand therefore my life disappears.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.73,1:40:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,殺人犯！\NMurderer!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.52,1:40:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要幫助！\NI need help!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.35,1:40:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,罪人.\NSinner!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.44,1:41:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,該死的牧師！\NDamn priest!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.83,1:41:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我好餓，給我些食物！\NI'm hungry!\NGive me some!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.46,1:41:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,給我，我好餓！\NGive me some!\NI'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.18,1:42:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,“{\u1}聖木木工{\u0}”\N"SACRED WOOD CARPENTERS"
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.60,1:43:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾，閣下...\NExcuse me, sir...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.61,1:43:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡沒什麼“閣下”.\NThere's no "sir" here.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.86,1:43:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,基督這個木匠都不傲慢，\NIf Christ the carpenter wasn't proud,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.86,1:43:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我又怎麼敢稱“閣下”？\Nthen why should I be?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.37,1:43:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我{\u1}約瑟{\u0}就好了.\NJust call me José.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.83,1:43:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾一下，{\u1}約瑟{\u0}...\NExcuse me, José...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.20,1:43:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要什麼嗎？你看上去...\NDo you need something?\NYou look
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.42,1:43:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就像快進棺材似得.\Nas if you could do\Nwith a coffin.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.47,1:43:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,“倘若我忘了你，\N"If I forget you,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.30,1:43:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，耶路撒冷，\N"O Jerusalem,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.47,1:43:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,情願我的右手忘記功能.”\N"let my right hand\Nforget its skill!"
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.85,1:43:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你都忘了嗎？\NHave you forgotten so much?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.27,1:43:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼折磨自己？\NWhy are you punishing yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.20,1:43:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,聖潔的長老，\NSaintly old man,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.66,1:43:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,請僱我工作！\Ngive me some work!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.12,1:44:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我磨這批椅子吧，我急於發貨.\NHelp me sand these chairs\NI have to deliver urgently.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.80,1:44:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,用心磨，我的兄弟.\NSand with your soul, my brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.59,1:45:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,神的一切道路，都通向真實.\NAll God's paths lead to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.03,1:45:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,約瑟，為什麼對我如此友善？\NJosé, why are you so good to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.29,1:45:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,“憂傷痛悔的心，\N"A broken and contrite heart,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.42,1:45:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你必不輕看.”\N"you will not despise."
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.79,1:45:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,詩篇第五十一.\NPsalm 51.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.96,1:45:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,詩篇第五十一.\NPsalm 51.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.01,1:45:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那你不會輕視我？\NBut don't you despise me?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.34,1:45:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不會！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.48,1:45:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在那海上，在那海上，\NOn the high sea!\NOn the high sea!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.07,1:45:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有個遠航的水手，\NThere was a sailor sailing
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.53,1:46:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他喜歡彈吉他，\NHe loved to play guitar
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.70,1:46:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,每當他思念，心愛的故鄉，\NAnd when he remembered\Nhis dear country
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.91,1:46:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他就拿起吉他，高聲歌唱，\NHe'd take his guitar and he'd start to sing
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.92,1:46:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在那海上，在那海上.\NOn the high sea!\NOn the high sea!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.01,1:46:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我們做好了百十把椅子.\NWe've got the hundred chairs!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.68,1:46:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,完工了.\NThe work is done.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.48,1:46:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我所以積蓄.\NThis is all I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.23,1:46:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-夠用嗎？\N-當然夠！\N- Will it be enough?\N- Of course!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.27,1:46:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我準備搭火車去{\u1}瓦爾帕萊索{\u0}，\NI'll take a train\Nto Valparaiso
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.32,1:46:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裡乘船回{\u1}托科皮亞{\u0}.\Nthen a boat to Tocopilla.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.53,1:46:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你！\NThank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.10,1:47:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨神之家！\NWelcome to the House of God!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.15,1:47:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了，你帶來了椅子.\NWonderful, you brought the chairs!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.44,1:47:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟們，{\u1}約瑟{\u0}先生帶來了椅子.\NBrothers,\NDon José brought the chairs!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.03,1:47:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,快過來！\NCome quickly!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.05,1:47:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，主啊，我的上帝，\NO Lord my God,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.10,1:47:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,當我思及你的雙手，\NWhen I, in awesome wonder,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.06,1:47:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,創造的世界，\NConsider all the worlds
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.98,1:47:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我驚奇無比.\NThy hands have made
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.49,1:48:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的重負都丟給主，\NCast your burden on the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.66,1:48:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他會替你承擔.\NAnd He will sustain you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.29,1:48:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他永遠不會遺棄\NHe shall never abandon
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.00,1:48:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那些倒下的人.\Nhe who falls.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.21,1:48:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,歌唱吧！\NLet us sing!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.54,1:48:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我的靈魂開始歌唱，\NThen sings my soul,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.46,1:48:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,神啊我的拯救者，為你而唱.\NMy Saviour God, to Thee
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.51,1:48:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你是多麼偉大，\NHow great Thou art,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.64,1:48:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你是多麼偉大，\NHow great Thou art,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.81,1:48:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我的靈魂開始歌唱，\NThen sings my soul
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.90,1:48:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,神啊我的拯救者，為你而唱.\NMy Saviour God, to Thee
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.94,1:48:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你是多麼偉大，\NHow great Thou art,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.95,1:48:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你是多麼偉大，\NHow great Thou art,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.16,1:48:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了，兄弟們.\NEnough, brothers!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.16,1:48:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,現在讓我們跳躍二十六下，\NNow let's jump 26 times
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.29,1:49:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,以感謝主的仁慈！\Nto thank our Lord for His mercy!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.75,1:49:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,一！\NOne!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.76,1:49:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,二！\NTwo!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.93,1:49:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,三！\NThree!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.34,1:49:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,四！\NFour!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.34,1:49:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,五！六！\NFive! Six!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.60,1:49:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,七！\NSeven!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.14,1:49:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,八！\NEight!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.47,1:49:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,九！\NNine!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.73,1:49:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,十！\NTen!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.64,1:49:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,十六！\NSixteen!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.56,1:49:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,十七！\NSeventeen!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.94,1:49:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,十八！\NEighteen!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.15,1:49:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,十九！\NNineteen!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.36,1:49:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,二十！二十一！\NTwenty! Twenty-one!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.53,1:49:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,二十二！\NTwenty-two!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.53,1:49:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,二十三！\NTwenty-three!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.82,1:49:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,二十四！\NTwenty-four!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.99,1:49:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,二十五！\NTwenty-five!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.99,1:49:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,二十六！\NTwenty-six!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.49,1:49:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哈利路亞！\NHallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.39,1:49:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟們，\NBrothers,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.32,1:50:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,善良的{\u1}約瑟{\u0}死了.\Nthe good José has died.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.15,1:50:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不！不！\NNo! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.40,1:50:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的，兄弟！\NNo, brother!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.45,1:50:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的兄弟死得多美.\NWhat a beautiful death our brother had.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.08,1:50:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他的每一跳都引領他進入神的心房，\NEach jump he gave brought him to the heart of God
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.79,1:50:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裡他延續生命.\Nand there he remained.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.92,1:50:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,為了每一把他免費獻給教堂的椅子，\NFor every free chair he offered to the church,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.05,1:50:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們感謝神，\Nlet us thank God,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.55,1:50:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他會為每個人準備一個天堂！\Nfor he deserves a paradise\Nfor each one!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.76,1:50:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們站在這椅子上.\NLet's climb on the chairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.47,1:50:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟姐妹們！\NBrothers and sisters!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.78,1:50:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,大家可以為我們...\NWhat do you think\Nof making a collection
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.16,1:50:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟的葬禮募捐嗎？\Nto pay for our brother's funeral?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.87,1:50:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好！\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.87,1:51:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,誰能居住在你神聖的山岡？\NWho may live on Your holy hill?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.25,1:51:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,誰能於心中洞悉真理.\NWho speaks the truth from his heart
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.76,1:51:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,誰能於心中洞悉真理.\NWho speaks the truth from his heart
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.06,1:51:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就這些了.\NThat's all there is.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.81,1:51:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣，他就能被埋在公墓.\NWith this, he will end up\Nin the communal grave.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.57,1:51:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,姐妹，\NSister,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.28,1:51:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我取出口袋里的東西，\Ntake out what's in this pocket
Dialogue: 0,1:51:36.28,1:51:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,交給牧師.\Nand give it to the Pastor.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.93,1:51:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,放入帽子里吧.\NPut it in the hat.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.42,1:52:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你這個傻瓜！你這個傻瓜！\NYou fool! You fool!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.22,1:52:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,打倒國際{\u1}猶太{\u0}教組織！\NDown with international Judaism!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.14,1:52:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,敬禮！\NHeil!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.02,1:52:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,敬禮！\NHeil!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.81,1:52:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}智利{\u0}屬於{\u1}智利{\u0}人！\NChile for the Chileans!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.15,1:52:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}智利{\u0}人屬於{\u1}納粹{\u0}！\NChileans for Nazism!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.74,1:52:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}納粹{\u0}屬於{\u1}智利{\u0}！\NNazism for Chile!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.45,1:52:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,納粹屬於{\u1}伊瓦涅斯{\u0}！\NNazism for Ibáñez!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.20,1:53:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,立定！\NHalt!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.80,1:53:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,張開你的手掌，朋友！\NExtend your hand, friend!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.97,1:53:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能，它萎縮了.\NI can't. It's withered.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.13,1:53:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,別胡扯！張開你的手，立刻！\NDon't mock! Extend your hand now!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.14,1:53:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我說了我不行.\NI'm telling you I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.47,1:53:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,該死的共產主義者！\NFucking communist!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.85,1:53:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,張開你的手，混蛋！\NExtend your hand, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.02,1:53:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我做不到.這雙手做不到！\NI can't do it. Nor with this one!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.77,1:53:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他在嘲弄我們的敬意！\NHe is mocking our salute!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.49,1:53:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都是兄弟.\NWe're all brothers.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.86,1:53:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,共產主義者的口號！\NCommunist propaganda!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.07,1:53:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,打倒他！\NBeat him up!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.97,1:54:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你這納粹白癡！\NYou stupid Nazi!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.98,1:54:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,說：“祝福{\u1}約瑟{\u0}先生！”\NSay: "Blessed be Don Jose!"
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.27,1:54:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,祝福{\u1}約瑟{\u0}先生.\NBlessed be Don Jose!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.90,1:54:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續！\NAgain!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:14.23,1:54:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-祝福{\u1}約瑟{\u0}先生.\N-繼續，否則我扯掉你的內臟！\N- Blessed be Don Jose!\N- Again, or I'll rip your guts out!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.24,1:54:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-祝福{\u1}約瑟{\u0}先生！\N-你！\N- Blessed be Don Jose!\N- You!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.49,1:54:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,祝福{\u1}約瑟{\u0}先生！\NBlessed be Don Jose!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.24,1:54:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,祝福{\u1}約瑟{\u0}先生！\NBlessed be Don Jose!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.79,1:54:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,祝福{\u1}約瑟{\u0}先生！\NBlessed be Don Jose!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.29,1:54:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,汪！汪！\NWoof! Woof!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.84,1:54:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,汪！\NWoof!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.31,1:54:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,祝福{\u1}約瑟{\u0}先生！\NBlessed be Don Jose!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.01,1:55:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}約瑟{\u0}先生是是誰？\NWho is Don José?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.35,1:55:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他是...\NHe's...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.48,1:55:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他是你的父親.\NHe's your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.02,1:55:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,坦白吧.\NConfess.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.48,1:55:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}約瑟{\u0}先生是誰？\NWho is Don José?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.32,1:55:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他是你的兄弟.\NHe's your brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.70,1:55:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}約瑟{\u0}先生是誰？\NWho is Don José?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.75,1:55:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他是你的兒子.\NHe's your son.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.67,1:55:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續！\NKeep going!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.34,1:56:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}約瑟{\u0}先生是誰？\NWho is Don José?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.47,1:56:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你.\NYou are.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.92,1:56:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把你的腦子崩出來！\NI'm going to blow\Nyour brains out!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:39.59,1:56:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}約瑟{\u0}先生是誰？\NWho is Don José?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.34,1:56:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是你，是我，是我們.\NYou are, I am, we all are.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.68,1:56:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了！\NEnough!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.55,1:56:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,坦白！\NConfess!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.22,1:56:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛你，{\u1}約瑟{\u0}先生！\NI love you, Don José!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.28,1:57:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,放鬆，\NEasy!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.49,1:57:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,放鬆，同志.\NEasy, comrade!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.29,1:57:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我來了.\NI'm here now.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.50,1:57:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看著我.\NLook at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.50,1:58:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你自由了，同志.\NYou're free, comrade.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.05,1:58:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你自由了.\NYou're free.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.76,1:58:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,獨裁結束了.\NThe dictatorship is over.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.59,1:58:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,無法解決危機，{\u1}伊瓦涅斯{\u0}拋棄了權力.\NUnable to solve the crisis,\NIbáñez has renounced power.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.31,1:58:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他逃去了阿根廷.\NHe fled to Argentina.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.23,1:58:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我想殺了他.\NI wanted to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.61,1:58:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你是個英雄，同志.你飽受折磨.\NYou are a hero, comrade.\NYou resisted torture.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.61,1:58:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你成家了嗎？\NDo you have a family?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.86,1:58:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是的.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:28.95,1:58:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我家在{\u1}托科皮亞{\u0}.\NMy family is in Tocopilla.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:32.78,1:58:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我們能做的，只有帶你回故鄉了.\NThe least we can do\Nis take you back to your village.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.04,1:58:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧.\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.75,1:58:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.29,1:58:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:51.64,1:58:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,當心點.\NBe careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.18,1:59:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸把我們都忘了.\NPapa has forgotten us.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.89,1:59:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我怕他再也不會回來.\NI'm scared he won't come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:39.98,1:59:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在害怕他不會回來？\NAre you scared\Nhe won't come back
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.40,1:59:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,還是在盼望他的歸來？\Nor don't you want him\Nto come back?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:47.07,1:59:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望只有我們兩個人，他根本不愛我.\NI like it just the two of us.\NHe doesn't love me.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.40,1:59:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你錯了.\NYou're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.78,1:59:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,把耳朵湊過來.\NPut your ear here.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.95,1:59:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,靠在我胸口.\NOn my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:59.54,2:00:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-聽到了嗎？\N-是的.\N- Can you hear it?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:02.50,2:00:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,它告訴你什麼？\NWhat is it telling you?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:05.08,2:00:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我的父親正在回家的路上.\NMy father is on his way home.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.55,2:00:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他很快就會到了！\NHe'll be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.21,2:00:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就這些？\NIs that all?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.13,2:00:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不，它還說他會非常愛我.\NNo. It says he'll love me a lot too.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:17.31,2:00:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了嗎？\NSee?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.10,2:00:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,當你感覺你的理智喪失了希望，\NWhen you feel\Nyour mind is losing hope,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:24.19,2:00:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,聽從你的心靈吧.\Nalways listen to your heart.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.25,2:00:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}薩若{\u0}！\NSara!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:09.61,2:01:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}傑{\u0}！\NJaime!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:12.40,2:01:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-是你.\N-別碰我.\N- It's you.\N- Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.03,2:01:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不值得這麼做.\NI don't deserve it!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:23.04,2:01:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我掌握了他.\NI had him in my hands
Dialogue: 0,2:01:25.58,2:01:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但它們卻癱瘓了！\Nbut they got paralysed!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.09,2:01:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我令你等待，\NI made you wait,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:33.84,2:01:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我無謂地犧牲了你.\NI sacrificed you needlessly.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:38.14,2:01:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不值得你的愛.\NI don't deserve your love.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:45.94,2:01:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我是個懦夫.\NI'm a coward.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.69,2:01:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不，爸爸！你是最強大的.\NNo, Papa! You're the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.32,2:01:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,男人永遠沒有恐懼.\NMen are never scared.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.45,2:01:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我的兒子！\NMy Son!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.74,2:02:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的兒子！\NMy Son!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.06,2:02:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的靈魂.\NYou are my soul.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:42.12,2:02:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的靈魂.\NYou are my soul.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:49.58,2:02:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我會永遠\NI will always
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.04,2:02:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,愛你.\Nlove you.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:08.77,2:03:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧，{\u1}薩若{\u0}.\NEnough, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:10.85,2:03:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人能治愈我.\NNobody will be able to cure me.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.52,2:03:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你能夠治愈你自己.\NYou can cure yourself.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:25.74,2:03:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你的神！\NLook at your god!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:33.79,2:03:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,看看這些你欽佩的惡魔！\NLook at the devil you admire!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.55,2:03:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:39.63,2:03:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你在{\u1}伊瓦涅斯{\u0}身上找到了，\NYou found in Ibáñez
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.72,2:03:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你在{\u1}斯大林{\u0}身上崇拜的一切.\Nall you admired in Stalin.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.81,2:03:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:52.85,2:03:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,而這就是你！\NAnd here you are!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:55.27,2:03:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你和他們一樣！\NYou are the same as they are!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:03.61,2:04:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,活在偽裝之下，\NYou have lived in the guise
Dialogue: 0,2:04:07.58,2:04:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,偽裝成一個暴君.\Nof a tyrant.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:10.91,2:04:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉.\NI am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:16.00,2:04:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這個在感受，在哭泣的男人，\NThis man who feels and cries,
Dialogue: 0,2:04:22.05,2:04:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這個人才是你.\Nthis man is you.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:27.35,2:04:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我們愛你，愛現在這個，\NWe love you\Nas you are now,
Dialogue: 0,2:04:32.06,2:04:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,更真實，\Nas, deep down,
Dialogue: 0,2:04:35.06,2:04:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,永恆不變的你.\Nyou have always been.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:40.78,2:04:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,做回自己吧.\NBe yourself again.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:01.88,2:05:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}傑{\u0}！\NJaime!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:05.99,2:06:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}托科皮亞{\u0}.\NTocopilla.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:04.30,2:07:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我由往昔扶搖遠去，\N{\i1}I soar away from the past,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:09.09,2:07:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}停靠於此刻的軀殼中，\N{\i1}Land in the body present,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.64,2:07:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}忍受著沉重而痛苦的歲月，\N{\i1}Bear the painful burden of years,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:17.10,2:07:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}就在心中留下那個孩子吧，\N{\i1}Yet in the heart keep the child,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:22.36,2:07:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}生命醞釀的果實，\N{\i1}As the bread of life,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:24.40,2:07:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}像一隻白色的云雀，\N{\i1}As a white canary,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:26.86,2:07:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}像一顆珍貴的寶石，\N{\i1}As a worthy diamond,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:29.28,2:07:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}像是清澈無比，纖毫不立，\N{\i1}As a lucidity without walls,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:31.91,2:07:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}沒有墻壁的阻隔，更沒有開敞的門窗，\N{\i1}Wide open doors and windows,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.83,2:07:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}於是起了風，{\i1}\NThrough which blows the wind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:37.75,2:07:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}只有風，\N{\i1}Only the wind,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:07:40.08,2:07:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}風而已.\N{\i1}Just the wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,2:08:47.27,2:08:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}烏克蘭{\u0}小屋.\NCasa Ukrania.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:48.36,2:08:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\u1}烏克蘭{\u0}小屋.\NCasa Ukrania.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:50.11,2:08:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的價格，\NOur prices
Dialogue: 0,2:08:51.53,2:08:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一個奇跡！\Nare a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:00.24,2:09:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,為健康乾杯！\NTo your health!
